reviewText: Styx Jones' Best PLAYBOY video by far! James Bond jets, Wild panthers, special secret cameos by ex nba baller javin johnson, special forces assistance, playmate joy Behrman and shot on 16mm film with some pretty sexy angles that playboy doesn't usually go for, i say CLASSIC. A favorite of HEF'S and i see why. Playmate Daphne Duplaix (from the jamie foxx show) scene alone is worth the price. Shot completely on location in South Florida with tons of secret Treasures ...  i'm daring to say ... Best PLAYBOY DVD in my collection and i got a few of em! Can't go wrong with this Title ... i saw the behind the scenes on the Playboy Channel years ago and i had to have this one .... actually i worked on this project so i understand the secrets revealed ...

Playboy presents fifteen fabulous femmes in and out of uniform in this tantalizing video compilation. From flight attendants to nurses and firefighters, your favorite occupations are covered--and uncovered! Actors: Joy E. Behrman, Daphne Duplaix, Christine Sheffner, Jessica Garvin (II), Dawn McFall
Ok, so it's not worthy of Oscar, but Girls offers Joy Behrman as a theater usher, nuff said! More usher..................

All the girls appearing in this video is sexy and lovely. However, Joy Behrman, who appears at the last part, is beautiful and the sexiest girl to me. Almost everytime I play this video, I always begin viewing from Joy's appearance. GOOD BUY VIDEO!

If Playboy ever decides to give these video away as a marketing tool take it. Then record your favorite TV show over it. Need to say more. Christie Hefner has taken Playboy to new heights. But here is a word of advice from  a big Playboy fan. Hire someone else to make the videos.
